intent.user_query: How can I use the `resusagescpuV` view to determine which CPUs experienced the highest I/O wait times on a specific date?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query for  on dbc: SELECT NodeID, cpuid, SUM(CPUIoWait) AS TotalIoWait FROM td_metric_svc.resusagescpuV WHERE TheDate = DATE '2024-11-29' GROUP BY NodeID, cpuid ORDER BY TotalIoWait DESC;

arguments.sql: SELECT NodeID, cpuid, SUM(CPUIoWait) AS TotalIoWait FROM td_metric_svc.resusagescpuV WHERE TheDate = DATE '2024-11-29' GROUP BY NodeID, cpuid ORDER BY TotalIoWait DESC;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
